            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>德国百年耳机名厂 Beyerdynamic 近日动作多多，最近推出了两款旗舰级耳机。早前小编已和大家开箱评测了 AMIRON 300 旗舰级入耳式耳机（<a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/11/18/beyerdynamic-amiron-300/mobile-music/headphones/">相关评测</a>）。近期气温开始转凉，终于可以换上头戴式耳机。如果你也喜欢头戴式耳机的话，以下小编就会和大家开箱看看 Aventho 300 真无线头戴封闭式耳机。</p><p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1276207" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc09925-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc09925-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc09925.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><h2></h2><h2>软硬便携袋兼备，提供保护性 + 便携选择</h2><p>开箱后可见 beyerdynamic 贴心地附送硬身保护盒和软袋，用家可以视乎需要选择使用保护性较高的硬盒，或是较轻便的软袋。</p><p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1276210" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc09927-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc09927-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc09927.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲内附硬身保护盒、软袋、3.5 mm 转 3.5 mm 线和 USB-C 充电线</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1276349" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc09953-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc09953-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc09953.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲耳机盒设计比较窄身</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1276214" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc09931-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc09931-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc09931.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲不会占用太多空位</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1276215" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc09930-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc09930-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc09930.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲盒内有硬身垫保护耳机</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1276350" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc09954-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc09954-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc09954.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲可有效保护耳机</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1276348" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc09956-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc09956-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc09956.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲另设软身便携袋</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1276222" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc09934-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc09934-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc09934.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲可进一步节省空位</p><br /><b>
